<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.6.5">
<l>nīṇṭāṉ kuṟaḷāy neṭuvā ṉaḷavu maṭiyār paṭumāḻ tuyarā yavellām</l>
<l>tīṇṭā mainiṉain timaiyō raḷavum celavait tapirā ṉatuvaṉ ṟiyummuṉ</l>
<l>vēṇṭā mainamaṉ ṟamareṉ tamarai viṉavap peṟuvā ralareṉ ṟulakēḻ</l>
<l>āṇṭā ṉavaṉkāṇ miṉiṉṟāyc ciyarā laḷaiveṇ ṇeyuṇṭāp puṇṭirun tavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who, as a dwarf, stretched up to the high heavens,</l>
<l rend="indent">the lord who placed [his foot] to reach up to the unblinking [celestials],</l>
<l>Resolving that all which becomes a deep sorrow</l>
<l rend="indent">that his devotees [might] suffer not touch [them],</l>
<l>Besides that, thinking, “If the servants of Death seek my servants,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will not obtain [them because of my] averting [it] earlier,”</l>
<l>The one who took control of the seven worlds, see,</l>
<l rend="indent">he is the one who was bound, having eaten the butter</l>
<l rend="indent">churned by the herder women today.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
